7.0, 857.0, 457.7]}, {"text": "Options expired and forfeited ..................................", "bbox": [136.1, 462.0, 550.5, 482.8]}, {"text": "-  $", "bbox": [661.4, 462.0, 698.8, 482.8]}, {"text": "-", "bbox": [810.0, 462.0, 857.0, 482.8]}, {"text": "Options exercised .....................................................", "bbox": [136.1, 487.0, 550.5, 507.8]}, {"text": "(30,398)  $", "bbox": [608.1, 487.0, 698.8, 507.8]}, {"text": "20.36", "bbox": [774.0, 487.0, 857.0, 507.8]}, {"text": "Outstanding and expected to vest at end of year  .......", "bbox": [136.1, 514.6, 550.5, 535.3]}, {"text": "564,044   $", "bbox": [606.6, 514.6, 698.8, 535.3]}, {"text": "34.90", "bbox": [774.0, 514.6, 846.0, 535.3]}, {"text": "8.10   $", "bbox": [931.8, 514.6, 996.0, 535.3]}, {"text": "30,786", "bbox": [1063.2, 514.6, 1128.8, 535.3]}, {"text": "Exercisable at end of year ..........................................", "bbox": [136.1, 545.8, 550.5, 566.6]}, {"text": "26,905   $", "bbox": [615.9, 545.8, 698.8, 566.6]}, {"text": "22.64", "bbox": [774.0, 545.8, 846.0, 566.6]}, {"text": "7.63   $", "bbox": [931.8, 545.8, 996.0, 566.6]}, {"text": "1,798", "bbox": [1072.7, 545.8, 1128.9, 566.6]}, {"text": "The weighted average grant-date fair value of options awarded during 2011, 2010 and 2009 was $49.61, $23.79", "bbox": [187.6, 585.8, 1127.1, 608.8]}, {"text": "and $6.27, respectively, using the Black-Sholes option-pricing model.  The intrinsic value of options exercised during", "bbox": [131.4, 609.8, 1126.9, 632.8]}, {"text": "2011, 2010 and 2009 was $1.5 million, $6.9 million and $3.1 million, respectively, based on the difference between", "bbox": [131.4, 633.6, 1127.4, 656.5]}, {"text": "the market price at the exercise date and the option exercise price.", "bbox": [131.4, 657.6, 686.7, 680.5]}, {"text": "Performance unit awards. During 2011, 2010 and 2009, the Company awarded performance units to certain of", "bbox": [187.6, 696.8, 1127.1, 719.8]}, {"text": "the Company's officers under the LTIP. The number of shares of common stock to be issued is determined by", "bbox": [131.4, 720.8, 1126.7, 743.8]}, {"text": "comparing the Company's total shareholder return to the total shareholder return of a predetermined group of peer", "bbox": [131.4, 744.8, 1125.9, 767.8]}, {"text": "companies over the performance period.  The performance unit awards vest over a 34-month service period.  The", "bbox": [131.4, 768.9, 1132.5, 791.9]}, {"text": "grant-date fair values per unit of the 2011, 2010 and 2009 performance unit awards are $134.68, $63.52 and $15.29,", "bbox": [131.4, 792.6, 1125.7, 815.6]}, {"text": "respectively, which amounts were determined using the Monte Carlo simulation method and are being recognized as", "bbox": [131.4, 816.7, 1126.9, 839.6]}, {"text": "compensation expense ratably over the performance period.  The Monte Carlo simulation model utilizes multiple", "bbox": [131.4, 840.7, 1126.5, 863.6]}, {"text": "input variables that determine the probability of satisfying the market condition stipulated in the award grant and", "bbox": [131.4, 864.7, 1127.3, 887.6]}, {"text": "calculates the fair value of the award. Expected volatilities utilized in the model were estimated using a historical", "bbox": [131.4, 888.7, 1126.4, 911.7]}, {"text": "period consistent with the remaining performance period of approximately three years. The risk-free interest rate was", "bbox": [131.4, 912.4, 1127.6, 935.4]}, {"text": "based on the U.S. treasury rate for a term commensurate with the expected life of the grant. The Company used the", "bbox": [131.4, 936.4, 1126.2, 959.4]}, {"text": "following assumptions to estimate the fair value of performance unit awards granted during 2011, 2010 and 2009:", "bbox": [131.4, 960.4, 1087.1, 983.4]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [651.2, 1004.0, 698.1, 1024.8]}, {"text": "2010", "bbox": [832.5, 1004.0, 879.5, 1024.8]}, {"text": "2009", "bbox": [1013.9, 1004.0, 1060.8, 1024.8]}, {"text": "Risk-free interest rate ...........................................................", "bbox": [131.4, 1053.5, 586.3, 1074.3]}, {"text": "1.32%", "bbox": [648.2, 1053.5, 701.4, 1074.3]}, {"text": "1.36%", "bbox": [829.5, 1053.5, 882.8, 1074.3]}, {"text": "1.33%", "bbox": [1010.9, 1053.5, 1064.1, 1074.3]}, {"text": "Range of volatilities .............................................................", "bbox": [131.4, 1078.6, 586.3, 1099.3]}, {"text": "50.2% - 84.1%", "bbox": [616.1, 1078.6, 733.3, 1099.3]}, {"text": "50.4% - 83.0%", "bbox": [797.5, 1078.6, 914.8, 1099.3]}, {"text": "47.1% - 73.0%", "bbox": [978.9, 1078.6, 1096.1, 1099.3]}, {"text": "The following table summarizes the performance unit activity for the year ended December 31, 2011:", "bbox": [187.6, 1115.6, 1040.3, 1138.5]}, {"text": "Number of", "bbox": [836.0, 1176.9, 927.4, 1197.6]}, {"text": "Units (a)", "bbox": [844.8, 1198.4, 918.7, 1219.1]}, {"text": "Weighted Average", "bbox": [960.8, 1155.4, 1114.2, 1176.1]}, {"text": "Grant-Date", "bbox": [988.9, 1176.9, 1090.9, 1197.6]}, {"text": "Fair Value", "bbox": [992.1, 1198.4, 1082.9, 1219.1]}, {"text": "Beginning performance unit awards ....................................................................................", "bbox": [131.4, 1249.4, 820.9, 1270.2]}, {"text": "263,729   $", "bbox": [867.8, 1249.4, 961.5, 1270.2]}, {"text": "28.91", "bbox": [1075.7, 1249.4, 1127.4, 1270.2]}, {"text": "Units granted ....................................................................................................................", "bbox": [139.1, 1274.4, 820.9, 1295.2]}, {"text": "43,495   $", "bbox": [877.1, 1274.4, 961.5, 1295.2]}, {"text": "134.68", "bbox": [1066.4, 1274.4, 1127.4, 1295.2]}, {"text": "Units vested (b) ................................................................................................................", "bbox": [139.1, 1299.4, 820.9, 1320.2]}, {"text": "(193,096)  $", "bbox": [860.1, 1299.4, 961.5, 1320.2]}, {"text": "16.25", "bbox": [1075.7, 1299.4, 1127.4, 1320.2]}, {"text": "Ending performance unit awards .........................................................................................", "bbox": [131.4, 1327.2, 820.9, 1347.9]}, {"text": "114,128   $", "bbox": [867.8, 1327.2, 961.5, 1347.9]}, {"text": "90.64", "bbox": [1075.7, 1327.2, 1127.4, 1347.9]}, {"text": "_____________", "bbox": [131.4, 1351.6, 270.0, 1374.6]}, {"text": "(a)", "bbox": [131.4, 1375.7, 156.8, 1396.5]}, {"text": "These amounts reflect the number of performance units granted. The actual payout of shares may be between zero percent", "bbox": [180.9, 1375.7, 1120.5, 1396.5]}, {"text": "and 250 percent of the performance units granted depending upon the total shareholder return ranking of the Company", "bbox": [180.9, 1397.5, 1121.3, 1418.2]}, {"text": "compared to peer companies at the vesting date.", "bbox": [180.9, 1419.0, 546.6, 1439.7]}, {"text": "(b)", "bbox": [131.4, 1440.5, 157.8, 1461.3]}, {"text": "On December 31, 2011, the service period lapsed on 178,289 of these performance unit awards. The lapsed units earned 2.5", "bbox": [180.9, 1440.5, 1120.5, 1461.3]}, {"text": "shares for each vested award representing 445,724 aggregate shares of common stock issued in 2012. On May 31, 2011,", "bbox": [180.9, 1462.0, 1120.5, 1482.8]}, {"text": "14,807 units lapsed as part of the Tunisian divesture and earned 2.5 shares for each vested award, representing 37,018 of", "bbox": [180.9, 1483.8, 1120.1, 1504.5]}, {"text": "aggregate shares of common stock.", "bbox": [180.9, 1505.3, 450.0, 1526.0]}]}